  <official_title>Randomized Controlled Trial to Evaluate Standard Thoracic Radiotherapy With or Without Concurrent Daily Low-dose Carboplatine in Elderly Patients With Locally Advanced Non-small Cell Lung Cancer (JCOG0301, NCSLC-Elderly-CBDCA-RT Phase III)</official_title>
