  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate whether radiotherapy with carboplatin will result in
      longer survival than radiotherapy alone in elderly patients with unresectable stage III
      NSCLC.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate whether radiotherapy with carboplatin will result in
      longer survival than radiotherapy alone in elderly patients with unresectable stage III
      NSCLC.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
